name: I tried to communicate with another planet and now my planet is being invaded
name_original: I tried to communicate with another planet and now my planet is being invaded
description:
I tried to communicate with another planet and now my planet is being invaded is a game developed by Rarysson. It was originally released in 2022.
You can play I tried to communicate with another planet and now my planet is being invaded on Web and PC. The game is sold via itch.io.
